rows.label: tlk401007_msg0002
rows.name:
The summit will be held inside this
battleship, so there's no need to
worry about attacks from the outside.

rows.label: tlk401007_msg0003
rows.name:
This door, the only entrance, will
not be opened until just before the
summit, to welcome Queen Lagert.

rows.label: tlk401007_msg0004
rows.name:
Not a single suspicious
person has passed.

rows.label: tlk401007_msg0005
rows.name:
In other words, we are
perfectly safe from attacks
from both inside and out.
